00:27:04.590 --> 00:27:08.420
Or alternatively, if it's not
a primary action for your

00:27:08.420 --> 00:27:11.040
particular activity, you can
go into the overflow.

00:27:11.040 --> 00:27:13.250
It's also fine to
put it in line.

00:27:13.250 --> 00:27:15.860
That's a valid option as well.

00:27:15.860 --> 00:27:20.110
I think a lot of the time, it
does suit the Action Bar very

00:27:20.110 --> 00:27:20.950
well, though.

00:27:20.950 --> 00:27:22.710
If it's primary, it goes
straight there

00:27:22.710 --> 00:27:23.840
in the visible action.

00:27:23.840 --> 00:27:25.730
If not, it can fall
into the overflow.

00:27:25.730 --> 00:27:31.340
So let me very quickly talk
through the two main ways that

00:27:31.340 --> 00:27:33.970
the Sharing action goes
into the Action Bar.

00:27:33.970 --> 00:27:37.250
So first of all, there's the
Share Action Provider.

00:27:37.250 --> 00:27:39.340
So it's kind of hard
to see here.

00:27:39.340 --> 00:27:41.060
Let's zoom in a little bit.

00:27:41.060 --> 00:27:42.920
This is how it looks.

00:27:42.920 --> 00:27:44.410
It's going to be kind of hard
to see on the video.

