00:30:12.630 --> 00:30:14.360
But as long as we call this
intent, you'll get the

00:30:14.360 --> 00:30:17.160
standard system behavior
there.

00:30:17.160 --> 00:30:21.270
And then, just down on the
bottom, again, for developers,

00:30:21.270 --> 00:30:22.230
implement this intent.

00:30:22.230 --> 00:30:25.190
Use sharecompat.intentbuildup.

00:30:25.190 --> 00:30:27.240
And then last quick point.

00:30:27.240 --> 00:30:28.960
You can go completely custom.

